{"tid":1927894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問題喺個制度（23條）","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T04:18:58.000Z","uid":265403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20d4c12fe29a5f6d73ee01b54ba32684c73887c3","tid":1927894,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"警暴係體制崩壞嘅一種呈現<br />\n背後問題喺個制度<br />\n一國兩制？<br />\n中共已經慢慢侵蝕緊下一代<br />\n唔好比六四發生喺香港<br />\n我地有責任要早d意識到個問題同埋解決<br />\n如何不在體制內抗爭<br />\n唔係9個月 而係17年了<br />\n<br />\n「他們堅信火還在門外<br />\n便永遠不會燒到房間裡」<br />\n<br />\n23條is coming to town<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候你想講句香港獨立 唯一出路都無得講<br />\n<br />\n反23條聯署（白宮）:<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/objection-article-23-hong-kong-basic-law-protect-freedom-speech-hong-kongers?fbclid=IwAR0FWah0JjVc2gXOh66PFz6qC3R3LgzzLIQ8zLdUdl9_RFK_hC6e78GI4PM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fobjection-article-23-hong-kong-basic-law-protect-freedom-speech-hong-kongers%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0FWah0JjVc2gXOh66PFz6qC3R3LgzzLIQ8zLdUdl9_RFK_hC6e78GI4PM&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f0ee993d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/objection-article-23-hong-kong-basic-law-protect-freedom-speech-hong-kongers?fbclid=IwAR0FWah0JjVc2gXOh66PFz6qC3R3LgzzLIQ8zLdUdl9_RFK_hC6e78GI4PM</a><br />\n<br />\n反23條聯署（網上流傳）：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ%2Fviewform&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=99ea6c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n香港係有自由嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左聯署 仲有其他可以做？開放討論下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grFv9PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrFv9PH.jpg&h=b303e382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a587393fb7a8755c050dd7682925186cb7cd2a0f","tid":1927894,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"不過其實六四已經發生咗喺香港<br />\n721 831同埋其他日子<br />\n政府否認自己嘅行為<br />\n暴力鎮壓巿民 剝奪應有嘅自由 權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747bb4e78a063dd7beb2b12fa43b228a26d08248","tid":1927894,"uid":305638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"認真po 推上去"},{"pid":"07941d42f52100c45849a064997f5a924fcd874b","tid":1927894,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747bb4e78a063dd7beb2b12fa43b228a26d08248","tid":1927894,"uid":305638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"認真po 推上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"魚魚 簽左未啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c44061b05d37027cd750066c566b3bab8624c3c","tid":1927894,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96897b27761964fe1b97bf56d5ad7a8977a52753","tid":1927894,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c44061b05d37027cd750066c566b3bab8624c3c","tid":1927894,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"路過請聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0329268f8de7e4d6c01f84aebd0da0b913f1b1","tid":1927894,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:49:47.000Z","msg":